## How To Add Scenarios

1. **Read the NORMATIVE CONTRACT MIRROR** — The feature file header contains the authoritative contract. Read it carefully.

2. **For each Rule, add 1-3 scenarios that test the guarantee:**
   - Use explicit ID tags: `@Rule(NN)` and `@Scenario(NN)`
   - Write scenarios in business language (Given/When/Then)
   - Focus on observable behavior, not implementation details

3. **Use this pattern:**
```gherkin
@Rule(01)
Rule: [Rule name from contract]

  @Scenario(01)
  Scenario: [Specific testable behavior]
    Given [precondition]
    When [action]
    Then [observable outcome]
```

