## Important Notes

- **This will create binding work** — Adding scenarios that use new step text will require bindings to be created in a follow-up mission. This is expected.
- **Don't implement bindings** — Just add the scenarios. The next mission will handle bindings.
- **Match existing step vocabulary** — Reuse step text from other features when possible to leverage existing bindings.
